    "causal_summary": "Code capability is split across sk-code (v3.5 flat surface-aware router) and sk-code-review (v1.5 standalone findings-first baseline already coupled to sk-code). No parent identity organizes code work, so the two collide in the advisor and the two-axis surface x activity router lives in one monolithic SKILL.md. This packet establishes sk-code as a parent hub with nested code modes, folding sk-code-review in, deciding the taxonomy by research and context evidence first.",
